description.en: CashPay ($CPZ) is an TRC20 token, built to tokenize and benefit the ecosystem of merchants, producers and consumers to grow the decentralised online retail. The stakeholders will receive multiple benefits as they become a part of the CashPay ecosystem. CashPay ($CPZ) is a unique token project, it has a full-fledged team of promoters and advisors with a clear vision and mission for CashPay token along with a solid media presence. CashPay facilitates transactions in the following three products – a Global Online Store, a Payment Gateway and a Merchant Wallet to serve all the layers of the e-commerce segment.
